text: Ian McElhinney (born 19 August 1948) is a Northern Irish actor and director. He has appeared in many television series. He is known for his role as Barristan Selmy in Game of Thrones, and as General Dodonna in Rogue One. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Belfast Category:Movie actors Category:Television actors Category:Radio actors Category:Movie directors
